pddl.prompt:
You are orchestrator. Your goal is:
{agents->orchestrator->goal}
Here is the public environment information:
{environment->public_information}
Here is the local plan produced by the vowel-capable agent:
{partial_vowel_plan}
Here is the local plan produced by the consonant-capable agent:
{partial_consonant_plan}
